{"tid":1617153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援義士賴雲龍","createTime":"2019-10-03T16:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T04:06:04.000Z","uid":18305,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aa10914ae62a6c9358eb6a81c6d386a1026d51c3","tid":1617153,"uid":18305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"【聲援義士賴雲龍】<br />\n<br />\n19歲義士賴雲龍因在7月14日沙田遊行及8月12日機場「警察還眼」行動，分別被控襲警、非法集結，及涉嫌襲擊《環時》記者付國豪。賴義士父母離異、一人獨居，在上次上庭時亦只有兩人聲援。<br />\n<br />\n賴義士將於明日早上九時三十分就涉嫌於沙田襲警一案上庭答辯，本會現呼籲各位中大人到場聲援賴義士，莫再讓義士感到孤單，審訊詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：10月4日（星期四）<br />\n時間：9:30am <br />\n地點：沙田裁判法院六樓（第七庭）<br />\n註：請預早一小時排隊取籌"},{"pid":"acf06ea66d2a65c8b05675690c07b0e99cdb3dfc","tid":1617153,"uid":70221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0311390f21e261d3942b469365e6e6ae459f632e","tid":1617153,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"6d02340fcbea6b72642b800b23403e9017d06b94","tid":1617153,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"一定會去"},{"pid":"9283120fb293f5ef3f5182a39e7d4e4713847367","tid":1617153,"uid":70221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e9934f1479c4493c95dcd297bdd447d0fc02f9","tid":1617153,"uid":168541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e84687498a6d3e4fe4283487ae72f71c52df2c6d","tid":1617153,"uid":311122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb6fef18cbbfa3d9f19b4f12b3e4c3ad8f7f38a1","tid":1617153,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:46:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fa1abd55fd29d08f4e98aedf6487d8f1ac17bb2","tid":1617153,"uid":146458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:50:01.000Z",